      "@type": "RepositoryObject",
      "name": "kurtakurtaka",
      "datePublished": "2016-11-08 01:36:17",
      "custom:translation": "Channel-billed cuckoo or Christmas bird",
      "custom:sentence": "Kurtakurtaka nganta marnana nyawa-ma Christmas time-ma, \"Ah Christmas-ku na marnana nyila-ma.\" Kuya-rnangulu kurru nyangani kamparrijang-kulu marlurluka-lu-ma kajijirri-lu-ma. Christmas nyila-ma lintarr ngurla marnana. ",
      "custom:sentenceTranslation": "The channel-billed cuckoo sings when Christmas is near. \"Ah it's singing for Christmas!\" That's what the men and women used to say in the old days. This bird lets us know that Christmas is coming.",
      "custom:photographerName": "Steve Parish",
      "custom:scientificName": "Scythops novaehollandiae",
